00:44:06.320 --> 00:44:08.320
as people who are robbers. We need to

00:44:08.320 --> 00:44:10.320
agree on something.

00:44:10.320 --> 00:44:12.320
Now Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam was also

00:44:12.320 --> 00:44:14.320
invited as one of the members.

00:44:14.320 --> 00:44:16.320
And he was a young man,

00:44:16.320 --> 00:44:18.320
it's reported he was in his 20s.

00:44:18.320 --> 00:44:20.320
And

00:44:20.320 --> 00:44:22.320
he went in and he was

00:44:22.320 --> 00:44:24.320
invited to witness this

00:44:24.320 --> 00:44:26.320
great treaty of human rights.

00:44:26.320 --> 00:44:28.320
What was it? It was known as

00:44:28.320 --> 00:44:30.320
Hilful Fudul,

00:44:30.320 --> 00:44:32.320
the pledge of the virtuous.

00:44:32.320 --> 00:44:34.320
What was the pledge of the virtuous?

00:44:34.320 --> 00:44:36.320
They agreed that we will all

00:44:36.320 --> 00:44:38.320
unite to help

00:44:38.320 --> 00:44:40.320
the one who is oppressed. That was

00:44:40.320 --> 00:44:42.320
the main treaty, the main

00:44:42.320 --> 00:44:44.320
point of that whole treaty. All of us

00:44:44.320 --> 00:44:46.320
will unite and we will help

00:44:46.320 --> 00:44:48.320
the one who is oppressed and we

00:44:48.320 --> 00:44:50.320
will challenge or fight

00:44:50.320 --> 00:44:52.320
the one who is the oppressor.

00:44:52.320 --> 00:44:54.320
Allahu Akbar. Later on Muhammad sallallahu

00:44:54.320 --> 00:44:56.320
alaihi wasallam says, I attended

00:44:56.320 --> 00:44:58.320
a treaty, a covenant

00:44:58.320 --> 00:45:00.320
in the period of ignorance

00:45:00.320 --> 00:45:02.320
