00:45:56.320 --> 00:45:58.320
So this is why Allah

00:45:58.320 --> 00:46:00.320
subhanahu wa ta'ala has mentioned to us

00:46:00.320 --> 00:46:02.320
in the Quran as well.

00:46:14.320 --> 00:46:16.320
Don't ever let the fact

